dict.key: Use Separate Colors for Light and Dark Mode

dict.string: Copy BQ schemas to different dataset
while read t; do bq show --schema --format=prettyjson "$t" > schema.json tbl_arr=("${(s:.:)t}") tbl=$tbl_arr[2] bq mk -t sandbox-jeff-ruane:aes_ipl.$tbl schema.json rm schema.json done < tables
aws s3 sync ~/Pictures/lightroom_catalog s3://jbrr-personal/photography --sse --storage-class GLACIER --region us-west-2
